1. Layout

    Alignment: Left, Center, Right.
    Width: Slider or input for custom width (percentage or pixels).
    Height: Slider or input for custom height (optional).
    Aspect Ratio: Lock/unlock aspect ratio toggle.
    Margin: Adjust margins around the image.
    Position: Inline, Block, Float Left/Right.

✅✅✅
2. Content

    Image URL: Textbox to add or edit the image's URL. ✅✅✅
    Alt Text: Input field for alternative text (for accessibility and SEO). ✅✅✅
    Caption: Option to add a caption below the image. ✅✅✅

3. Style

    Border: Add border styles (e.g., width, color, style). ✅✅✅
    Shadow: Add shadow effects to the image.
    Opacity: Adjust transparency level. ✅✅✅
    Border Radius: Add rounded corners. ✅✅✅
    Filters: Apply effects (e.g., grayscale, brightness, contrast). ✅✅✅

✅✅✅
4. Padding

    Padding: Adjust padding inside the image's container. ✅✅✅

